[thinking] **Considering test structures**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about how to set up the helper file properly since it’s public. There’s a question about “one-to-one mapping”—maybe it’s not allowed? An alternative is to use the public class HtmlAdapterServer as the JUnit test itself and also as a helper. But if the test class is to be the helper, would it be better to separate them? I wonder if using an inner package could be a solution. I have a lot to explore here!
